# ── OS / editor noise ──────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── Python ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# ── Personal tax data — NEVER commit ───────────────────────────
# Real tax-year folders (2022/, 2023/, 2024/, 2025/, …) hold private
# documents: source PDFs, extracted facts.json, and reports.
# Only the 20xx/ example structure is tracked.
/20[0-9][0-9]/

# Safety net: never leak a tax PDF from anywhere in the repo.
*.pdf

# Defense-in-depth: never commit derived tax artifacts from anywhere,
# even if they ever land outside a year folder.
*_facts.json
*_report*.html

# What IS committed: README.md, CLAUDE.md, the .claude/ skills & agents
# (which now hold pdf_triage.py + facts.schema.json), and the 20xx/ example.
